3. Creating users and groups 
Manual Method:
	groupadd oinstall 
	groupadd dba 
	
	useradd oracle 
	usermod -g oinstall -G oinstall,dba oracle
Automated Method:
	yum install oracle* --skip-broken 
	yum install -y oracle-database-preinstall-19c --skip-broken
 
 
